                </button>
              </h3>
              <div
                class="faq-item__answers"
                id="faq-a-0"
                role="region"
                aria-labelledby="faq-q-0"
                data-faq-panel
                hidden
              >
                <div class="faq-item__pad">
                  <div class="faq-item__bubble">
                    <p class="faq-item__answer">
                      Izybiz is built on a simple belief: AI projects don't fail
                      because of the technology, but because no one owns both
                      the business intent and delivery. With 20 years in
                      business management, we ensure AI solutions are delivered,
                      adopted, and drive real business outcomes.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="faq-item" data-faq-item>
              <h3 class="faq-item__heading">
                <button
                  class="faq-item__question"
                  type="button"
                  aria-expanded="false"
                  aria-controls="faq-a-1"
                  id="faq-q-1"
                  data-faq-trigger
